name: Wobbler
description:
Interactive Tool inspired by SlitScreen Tech.
Also upload your own pictures!

Please see DrAbstract's ↑ ↑ ↑ creations for more!

The app uses the ZIM rarity() function.
We use the ZIM chop() function to slice the picture
and we animate using the ZIM Noise class.
For more information on ZIM see https://zimjs.com 
a JavaScript Canvas framework to code creativity!
